nodes.text: What happens to children flying alone?
Feedback Commenter (10): What happens to children flying alone?
Annot: What happens to children flying alone?
The airlines require that a companion (an employee of the airline) be assigned (for a fee) to children under a certain age for the duration of their travels.

How do the children just over the cutoff fend for themselves?
